<br>
This area is soloable by lower levels who are NOT kos there, but what about those of us who are?  Does anyone know if the other bots will jump in to assist Gabbie when a lvl 49 kos player attacks her?  And <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>   if</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> by chance they don't assist her, what happens when I sit down to med while waiting on the next spawn?<br>
<br>
I have made a newbie rogue just to go down and look around the area... wanted to see if there might be a fairly clear area near the castle so I could go in invis'ed, stop before castle, and make pet to fight my way into the castle.  It seems there isn't a really good spot.  This trip will most likely involve making pet at zone and clearing a path.<br>
<br>
Basically, I wanta know if I will be able to pluck one bot at a time at the castle... at lvl 49... and being already kos.<br>
<br>
Any advice? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <p><img src=http://www.geocities.com/kimmi_sc/teldiva_grimleux.jpg>
