<br>
My advice to you is to tell your pet to guard outside the castle. A good pull spot is in the tunnel entrance facing the castle gates.<br>
<br>
There should be two bots standing guard.<br>
Pull one with Nullify magic and hope the other doesn't come.<br>
If they do, no big deal, my pet handled both of them easily. (was using 44 earth at the time)<br>
After the two sentries are dead, go into the castle and pull each gnome with Nullify magic. Seems to work almost 100% of the time and you will only have to fight one gnome at a time.<br>
<br>
Maybe because they are all low, I dunno, but it worked every time I did it, so I hope you have the same success.<br>
<br>
